==Other versions of the legendarium==
A late manuscript of what would later become [[Appendix A]] lists Aranarth's date of birth as {{TA|1938}},<ref name=Elendil/> but in the same manuscript,<ref>{{PM|Elendil}}, manuscript C, The Northern Line of Arnor: the Isildurioni, 24. Araphant</ref> as well as in [[Appendix A]], "Gondor and the Heirs of Anárion"<ref name=Ondoher/> and in the [[Appendix B|Tale of Years]],<ref name=TA1940/> his parents' wedding year is given as {{TA|1940}}. It is possible that the year of birth being two years before the year of marriage of his parents, who were of royal descent, was an oversight.

